body_html:
Hi @kanul,

The issue originally described should be resolved.

It seems that you are using a mobilenet_v2 implementation contains an unsupported operation. What mobilenet_v2 implementation are you using? The code I have tried out is here: https://github.com/tensorflow/models/blob/master/research/slim/nets/mobilenet/mobilenet_v2.py .

Make sure you are freezing an eval graph and not a training graph and provide the correct input and output nodes when freezing as well.
